creator: FishAnn07 Production
descriptionHtml:
WPS Connect Wifi is a beta featured utility focused for Analyzing and testing Authorized Networks only !
and also helps you to make your WiFi Router More Secure.

With this app you can try to connect to Authorized WiFi networks which have WPS protocol enabled.

Note : This Application is made for education purpose only , Only for Testing on Authorized Network (Your Own Wifi Router), I am not responsible for any misuse.


Beta Features :
No Root

Features

1.Theme (only for devices below Android 9.0)
*Dark Theme
*Light Theme

In Android 9.0 and above Android Version theme is system default, that mean whenever you turn on dark mode the App will set to dark theme theme too.

2. Graphical representation of WiFi Signals
3. Channel Analyzer -
helps you to detect how many devices connected to specific channel, this feature works even if you are not connected to WiFi.
4. Show WiFi Passwords
5. Offline Pin Generator

Guide to make your WiFi Secure
*Disable WPS in your Router to make it more secure and use Strong password.

Note: Prior to an assessment, understand that it serves the application.
